{
  "stem": "18626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all the tailors, my uncles were tailors, they walked in the shops.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a lot of my friends worked in the shops.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, that big man, that leader Rabinowitz, had a son approximately my age, Mr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rabinowitz said to me, Maishke, teach my boy a little wood-turning too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a roll of lathes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to teach him all the time, how to hold a tool, how to cut.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were starting to work in the werkstatten.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was turning parts for toys, wooden toys, airplanes, tanks, trucks, bombs, wooden bombs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a department of artists in the same werkstatten who did the painting, and put on the swastika, you know, on the tanks, and the wooden toys.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the tank was all finished, it looked like a miniature real German tank.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had designers in the werkstatten, Jewish designers, and architects who drew, you know, exactly how the tanks, the toy tanks or the toy trucks, had to be made.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then it was finished, it was excellent toys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans were happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they used to-- they used to pack it in cartons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was shipped to Germany for the German children, and for the German army's kids to play with toys made by the Jews in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While our children were killed and slaughtered, we had to make for the German children toys, for them to play in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was heart-breaking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think about 10 hours or something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto, we used to get portions of bread, like for a family, you know, a couple loaves-- in the first months, then it start to get worse, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
